<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: Rimatomics -->
  <RimatomicsActivate.label>「边缘核能」</RimatomicsActivate.label>
  <!-- EN: A probe has been detected in orbit! It seems to be sending signals to the surface; maybe we can decipher its message. -->
  <RimatomicsActivate.description>已检测到在轨道上的探测器，似乎有信号发送到地面，或许我们可以破译它。</RimatomicsActivate.description>
  <!-- EN: You open a connection to the probe and a recorded message starts to play.\n\nSomeone with the slimy demeanour of a used bionics salesman claims to represent a trading faction known as "Rimatomics".\n\nAs he makes his sales pitch, exabytes of data begins flooding into the console. He explains that he's sending blueprints to construct a Rimatomics research bench, which you can use to purchase plans for some of their technology or request trade ships.\n\nCheck the Rimatomics tab in the architect menu. -->
  <RimatomicsActivate.discoveredLetterText>你已连接到探测器，开始播放预先录制的消息。\n\n一个蹩脚的拟人声自称来自「边缘核能」贸易公司。\n\n它似乎在推销某种产品，通讯台台接收到大量数据。它解释说正在向殖民地发送「边缘核能」研究台的制造蓝图，你可以使用该研究台购买「边缘核能」技术和呼叫「边缘核能」贸易船。\n\n请查看「建造」选项卡的「边缘核能」一栏。</RimatomicsActivate.discoveredLetterText>
  <!-- EN: Rimatomics Unlocked! -->
  <RimatomicsActivate.discoveredLetterTitle>「边缘核能」解锁！</RimatomicsActivate.discoveredLetterTitle>
  
</LanguageData>